{"tid":1854293,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"【養兔潮流】兔兔的視覺好特別 !!","createTime":"2020-01-31T11:50:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-07T08:30:24.000Z","uid":197098,"like":2,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"e3d32f9cead4b668baeb17d50a4c578beeaf6a5c","tid":1854293,"uid":197098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T11:50:05.000Z","msg":"兔子<span style=\"color: gold;\">側面看某東西就代表正面看某東西</span>。牠們正前方和下方是盲點，除了這兩個盲點外，牠們幾乎可以看到360度。(所以有時食物在牠下巴下面看不到)&nbsp;<span style=\"color: gold;\">你在牠後面也會看到你</span>。兔子只有向著前方大約30度範圍，才可以有立體影像。牠們的脊椎就像軟骨那麼脆弱, 另外也有遠視。所以牠們不是無視你，你是在他們視線範圍之內。<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/EwUbFnW9Qa4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FEwUbFnW9Qa4&d=6xH2G4nGFyEJ53rX7DpuManyrFheAedOz%2Bkyyi3ikZI%3D&h=4c0d997b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/EwUbFnW9Qa4</a>"},{"pid":"c1576a4284d0e75e4ec10cbd2103032c32e3491b","tid":1854293,"uid":317233,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e3d32f9cead4b668baeb17d50a4c578beeaf6a5c","tid":1854293,"uid":197098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T11:50:05.000Z","msg":"兔子<span style=\"color: gold;\">側面看某東西就代表正面看某東西</span>。牠們正前方和下方是盲點，除了這兩個盲點外，牠們幾乎可以看到360度。(所以有時食物在牠下巴下面看不到)&nbsp;<span style=\"color: gold;\">你在牠後面也會看到你</span>。兔子只有向著前方大約30度範圍，才可以有立體影像。牠們的脊椎就像軟骨那麼脆弱, 另外也有遠視。所以牠們不是無視你，你是在他們視線範圍之內。<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/EwUbFnW9Qa4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FEwUbFnW9Qa4&d=6xH2G4nGFyEJ53rX7DpuManyrFheAedOz%2Bkyyi3ikZI%3D&h=4c0d997b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/EwUbFnW9Qa4</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T11:51:20.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">武肺背後嘅第三次世界大戰：諜戰丶生化戰丶經濟戰<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1854117\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1854117</a><br />\n</span></strong>"},{"pid":"6221bc87bac837414a1fc006500c75100acbffb3","tid":1854293,"uid":48222,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T12:04:08.000Z","msg":"樓主做咩唔打英文"},{"pid":"710382d6682a1d26718e7a15224ad9872d914bcb","tid":1854293,"uid":197098,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T12:35:07.000Z","msg":"我有個女仔朋友3年前被男友分手後一直好憂鬱，成日哭又唔食嘢，瘦咗30磅，她以為可以同個男仔結婚永遠幸福🤦🏻&zwj;♂️😣上年7月領養了一隻白兔，希望可以分散自己冇咁憂鬱，點知好快趣識咗個男仔，個男仔好愛佢，家境又富有，佢又鐘意個男仔，佢地而家結咗婚，Honeymoon喺馬爾代夫過，女仔好幸福，兩個住喺貝沙灣5500呎洋房，佢哋另外貝沙灣仲有3個Apartment單位收租(有一個係個男送比個女)，男仔老豆喺內地有幾閒廠，仲有一個超大幾十萬平方呎嘅田地種蕃薯水果。我個女仔friend好信風水，好鐘意睇D男仔八字同自己夾唔夾，結咗婚後有個風水師同佢講原來隻白兔旺佢同佢老公，話佢好適合養兔，我話咁都得 🤣"},{"pid":"19b24a6d39476274e6a74890e6412b043b3e6b6c","tid":1854293,"uid":100016,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T13:44:47.000Z","msg":"收皮啦白卡佬"},{"pid":"a060a4a05882f3e6c21d2919b1b8b45243bf1953","tid":1854293,"uid":317376,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T13:53:25.000Z","msg":"你唔可以話養兔潮流囉！兔唔係過左潮流就換嘅野！"},{"pid":"3f085f46c460d4d5eb8e335b09624988fce33544","tid":1854293,"uid":197098,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"a060a4a05882f3e6c21d2919b1b8b45243bf1953","tid":1854293,"uid":317376,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T13:53:25.000Z","msg":"你唔可以話養兔潮流囉！兔唔係過左潮流就換嘅野！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T14:11:26.000Z","msg":"同意👍🏻😊"},{"pid":"f5f2f00c385912b46a205b36d1037956e4d7d6b7","tid":1854293,"uid":197098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T16:51:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"576af115fb036b8404c5fec5cf95c90084fb24fc","tid":1854293,"uid":293838,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T17:12:36.000Z","msg":"原來你識打中文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b143619d008b4727bb81db65424cc647ae1af43e","tid":1854293,"uid":197098,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T03:40:59.000Z","msg":"Happy new year! I wish all your endeavors in 2020 are successful! <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/yipes1000.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35d23110fc6c0d621df2a305dfab325aab5147cc","tid":1854293,"uid":197098,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T04:06:39.000Z","msg":"I hope all your dreams come true in 2020- onwards and upwards !"},{"pid":"f94e6bb5f7c60b0565ba5a35e6edf21ca822ac3f","tid":1854293,"uid":213812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T04:14:13.000Z","msg":"拉"},{"pid":"88ba95ff72a66464ce3cca05eab3cd82f5367d65","tid":1854293,"uid":197098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T05:46:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a5d9846f233a8bc0e947f782499b2cc2ee45c03","tid":1854293,"uid":197098,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T06:16:34.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">兔子的睡窩被貓霸佔了 !</span></span><br />\n<br />\n兔子是被捕獵的動物(prey animal)，在大自然內是每個捕獵者(predator)的目標，沒有自然本能去攻擊他人，牠們的脊椎就像軟骨那麼脆弱。<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/2HMWjTXFwuY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F2HMWjTXFwuY&d=6xH2G4nGFyEJ53rX7DpuManyrFheAedOz%2Bkyyi3ikZI%3D&h=d2354f99\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/2HMWjTXFwuY</a>"},{"pid":"c1ab4788349b1485c881d22e819985e2fcf24df5","tid":1854293,"uid":197098,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T06:47:58.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">狗狗搶嘢食, 兔兔毫無還擊之力 !</span></span><br />\n<br />\n兔子側面看某東西代表正面看某東西，你在牠後面也會看到你。(你可想像正前方是盲點，看得最清楚，前腳移動有限，又怎會攻擊到他人？）😭😆🙈:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=JKwW65LcLIg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DJKwW65LcLIg&d=6xH2G4nGFyEJ53rX7DpuManyrFheAedOz%2Bkyyi3ikZI%3D&h=0d2ec93f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=JKwW65LcLIg</a>"},{"pid":"0d593a2d9b8ef180a000fb1f3ffcbc8dbbac897c","tid":1854293,"uid":201604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T06:50:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3bba8bc38f2460c4055356076be8f9b23e4260b","tid":1854293,"uid":197098,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T09:00:26.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">兔子拚命地拯救一隻被困住的貓! 真感人! ☺</span></span><br />\n<br />\n兔子是一種好心境平靜的動物，很多人覺得牠們咀嚼食物的聲音很治癒。如果你家的兔子有攻擊性，這不是牠的本性，而是後天環境和飼養方式影響。兔子亦被作為情緒和心靈支持動物(emotional support animal)，即是主人有醫生的證明，帶着小動物作伴，心靈才得到慰藉。<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/ydwwZtQyuiU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FydwwZtQyuiU&d=6xH2G4nGFyEJ53rX7DpuManyrFheAedOz%2Bkyyi3ikZI%3D&h=b098d0bc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/ydwwZtQyuiU</a>"},{"pid":"87c7b739c56a5557ef9419a87e61d870c55bbaa6","tid":1854293,"uid":197098,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T11:18:01.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">兔子發夢同主人玩：<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/s-7b9X5x_Ro\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fs-7b9X5x_Ro&d=6xH2G4nGFyEJ53rX7DpuManyrFheAedOz%2Bkyyi3ikZI%3D&h=87f82d53\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/s-7b9X5x_Ro</a></span></span>"},{"pid":"5c458090fab0ceaa0780bd7e8c76e0d87c372569","tid":1854293,"uid":197098,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T12:05:20.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><ins>兔子是應該要被絕育...(寵物兔)</ins></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><em>根據美國兔子協會(House Rabbit Society)</em></span>:<br />\n<br />\n1. 兔子是被捕獵動物(Prey animal), 是大自然內每個捕獵者(Predator)的目標, 狗吠聲、消防車叫聲、小孩尖叫、雷暴等也會嚇驚兔子, 所以不建議帶出外散步。兔子是全世界其中一個最多被棄養的動物(在美國排第3最多被棄養), 很多人將牠放生, 這樣會令兔子十分恐慌, 而且沒有覓食能力(寵物兔和野兔是不同), 有些人送給兔協, 但容納不到那麼龐大的數目。<br />\n<br />\n2. 絕育後會大大減少因荷爾蒙控制而霸地盤，不會隨地去廁所 (兔子是不需要訓練去廁所，只要廁所內有紙棉和乾草和夠大便可以, 建議用貓廁所)<br />\n<br />\n3. 荷爾蒙減少令攻擊性減少，更加溫馴和親人，也會活得更開心。如果想將2隻兔合養(做夫妻/好朋友)要先絕育才容易建立關係, 否則有機會打架！<br />\n<br />\n4. 兔子是很容易患上生殖器病動物，所以絕育會令到更健康和長壽！<br />\n<br />\n5. 減少過量繁殖(和棄養後所面對的困境)，繁殖得快和多。"},{"pid":"2b99b2141abfa6888117465f378f69ca6c4828b1","tid":1854293,"uid":197098,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T13:31:31.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">兔子發夢飲水:<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/koTWmdwLlp8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FkoTWmdwLlp8&d=6xH2G4nGFyEJ53rX7DpuManyrFheAedOz%2Bkyyi3ikZI%3D&h=9661b30c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/koTWmdwLlp8</a></span></span>"},{"pid":"65e13a3aa141a06bfef62ec43d7fd5dd9a60e52d","tid":1854293,"uid":197098,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T15:18:59.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">兔仔入樽破世界健力士紀錄 !<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/XNJmeXb4Y0A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FXNJmeXb4Y0A&d=6xH2G4nGFyEJ53rX7DpuManyrFheAedOz%2Bkyyi3ikZI%3D&h=6760e0e3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/XNJmeXb4Y0A</a></span></span>"},{"pid":"0f70f7417a28713c986b22d44cc05b9c7194c4ca","tid":1854293,"uid":1247,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T15:20:38.000Z","msg":"兔兔這麼可愛"},{"pid":"78458699b9e2ae7cd5b214e0eb23ab0684756fe4","tid":1854293,"uid":197098,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T15:20:47.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">領養了兔子,瘋狂跳兔子舞!</span></span><br />\n<br />\n跳兔子舞(Binky)是兔子最開心的狀態。這是告訴你是一個好主人，代表牠很喜歡現時的環境和生活：<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Mu27kYckovg0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FMu27kYckovg0&d=6xH2G4nGFyEJ53rX7DpuManyrFheAedOz%2Bkyyi3ikZI%3D&h=ec070385\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Mu27kYckovg0</a>"},{"pid":"2f1fe9a27a020d4f2039d06f0419d0af72df45bc","tid":1854293,"uid":197098,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0f70f7417a28713c986b22d44cc05b9c7194c4ca","tid":1854293,"uid":1247,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T15:20:38.000Z","msg":"兔兔這麼可愛"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T15:23:25.000Z","msg":"Indeed"},{"pid":"a3009a6ecb20c5c2a48f814fe4fb321defb07e9f","tid":1854293,"uid":197098,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T02:28:39.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">兔子會不會叫? 是會的....</span></span><br />\n<br />\n開心時會「<span style=\"color: gold;\">屋屋</span>」聲叫：<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/mPoSiZmzo58\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FmPoSiZmzo58&d=6xH2G4nGFyEJ53rX7DpuManyrFheAedOz%2Bkyyi3ikZI%3D&h=592fe3df\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/mPoSiZmzo58</a><br />\n<br />\n不滿時會<span style=\"color: gold;\">咕咕叫</span>。後腳大力踏地代表不滿，但也可以代表驚慌覺得有危險，要看當時的情況。在大自然內，兔子後腳大力踏地是用來警告其他兔仔(包括你)有危險。當兔子遇到巨大驚慌或痛苦也會尖叫，例如被捕獵者(predator)追殺和吃的時候，當然這情況是很慘。<br />\n<br />\n以下video 可看到<span style=\"color: gold;\">咕咕叫</span>。當牠用鼻碰主人的手然後縮低代表想被撫摸:<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Z8wfR7k3844\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FZ8wfR7k3844&d=6xH2G4nGFyEJ53rX7DpuManyrFheAedOz%2Bkyyi3ikZI%3D&h=355946f2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Z8wfR7k3844</a>"}]}